o-th%E1%BA%A7n-C%E1%BB%AFu-th%E1%BB%8B-chi-nh%E1%BA%ADm-L%C3%A2m-Thao/poem-zOVPUyRztgwIA2aCfewRLg">Tống bảo thần Cữu thị chi nhậm Lâm Thao - 送寶臣舅氏之任臨洮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Thanh-Ti%C3%AAu/author-p0qkGr9Bb8NsSr-KiQXZtw">Lương Thanh Tiêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nghi%E1%BB%85m/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-T%C3%A2n-Ti%C3%AAu-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nhai-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam/poem-8h9bq7BiGA6048d4JjXN7w">Tống Lý Trọng Tân, Tiêu Phương Nhai xuất sứ An Nam - 送李仲賓蕭方崖出使安南其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nghi%E1%BB%85m/author-WBjKpsbZn7AL_s86vNKjZA">Trần Nghiễm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/V%C5%A9-t%E1%BB%85-ti%E1%BB%83u-ch%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc/poem-6EMhTmNEyjDGTT_lY6Qomg">Vũ tễ tiểu chước - 雨霽小酌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-ZKcZplnWb1erBy2eMui9_A">Xuân nhật hữu cảm kỳ 1 - 春日有感其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br></div>	</div>
